"{\"uid\": \"housingwire.com-articles-real-estate-agents-olympics-navigating-business-practice-changes\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"It is fitting that the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris are the backdrop for the final two weeks leading up to when the real estate industry will undergo its largest structural change in decades - a feat of near-Olympic proportions.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 54, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999863498489, \"rank\": 1.3650287689062592e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 19, \"to\": 43}, {\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 57, \"to\": 69}, {\"ngram\": \"the final two weeks\", \"from\": 74, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"the real estate industry\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"its largest structural change\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 180}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"a feat\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 200}, {\"ngram\": \"near-Olympic proportions\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the athletes in Paris, Realtors and brokers across the U.S. have been busy training and preparing to be ready for Aug. 17, the date on which the terms of theNational Association of Realtors'(NAR) nationwidecommission lawsuitsettlement agreementare set to go into effect.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 254, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999863498489, \"rank\": 1.3650287689062592e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"Realtors\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"brokers\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"busy training\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"the date\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"the terms\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"theNational Association\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"Realtors'(NAR\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \") nationwidecommission lawsuitsettlement\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"effect\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the terms of the settlement, agents will no longer be allowed to share their seller's offers of buyer broker compensation on an MLS.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multiple_listing_service\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.021825355155337e-23, \"text\": \"MLS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multiple_listing_service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multiple_listing_service\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the terms\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"the settlement\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"agents\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"their seller's offers\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"buyer broker compensation\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will also have to obtain a signedbuyer representation agreementprior to a buyer's first home tour.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a signedbuyer representation\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"a buyer's first home tour\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In only a matter of weeks, real estate professionals nationwide will find out whether their training has paid off.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only a matter\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"real estate professionals\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"their training\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Minnetonka, Minnesota, Bryan VantHof - who is a member of theRE/MAX Advantage Plus-brokeredThe Minnesota Real Estate Team- said he feels ready to handle whatever the industry and the housing market throw at him.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999751052266371, \"rank\": 2.0520804545252102e-05, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\"}, {\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.9999999993842721, \"rank\": 3.899716613019519e-10, \"text\": \"Bryan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Minnetonka\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"MAX\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"Plus\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"the industry\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"the housing market\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was nervous at first, but I enjoy a challenge, and at this stage, I feel like I have got a strategy in place that is really going to set me apart from people who are still trying to figure it out,\\\" VantHof said.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"a strategy\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"VantHof\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His confidence did not just come out of nowhere.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His confidence\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"VantHof has spent several months training to prepare for the business practice changes.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"VantHof\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"several months\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"the business practice changes\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have had so many meetings,\\\" VantHof said.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many meetings\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"VantHof\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And in those meetings, we have had different leaders come in and talk about how these rule changes impact things from aFannie Mae,Freddie Mac, VA or FHA standpoint.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mae\", \"score\": 0.999981410081991, \"rank\": 1.8590263544042912e-05, \"text\": \"Mae\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mae\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mae\"}, {\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freddie_Mac\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Freddie Mac\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freddie_Mac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freddie_Mac\"}, {\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Veterans_Affairs\", \"score\": 0.99999998735575, \"rank\": 1.2586346449802047e-08, \"text\": \"VA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Veterans_Affairs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Department_of_Veterans_Affairs\"}, {\"begin\": 1636, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Housing_Administration\", \"score\": 0.9999999997653504, \"rank\": 2.1527361794077966e-10, \"text\": \"FHA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Housing_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Housing_Administration\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those meetings\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"different leaders\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"these rule changes\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also brought in a forms specialist, who really dug into the new forms to really explain them to us, so we know when and how to use each one and so we can explain the contracts to our clients in plain English.\\\"\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a forms specialist\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"the new forms\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"each one\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"the contracts\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"our clients\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"plain English\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"VantHof said RE/MAX Advantage Plus is planning on using the forms provided byMinnesota Realtors, which did not come out until recently, leaving him with just a few weeks to fully digest the contents of the forms.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"VantHof\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"MAX Advantage Plus\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"the forms\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"byMinnesota Realtors\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"just a few weeks\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"the contents\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"the forms\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were given a few months to kind of play all of this out in our minds, and then with like two weeks of notice, we get hit with all the forms and how procedures will work in our state - because every state has its own laws, which changes what the settlement looks like in each state,\\\" VantHof said.\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few months\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"our minds\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"two weeks\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2184}, {\"ngram\": \"notice\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"all the forms\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"procedures\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"our state\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"every state\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"its own laws\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"the settlement\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"each state\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"VantHof\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Training on forms has been a central focus of brokerages across the country.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Training\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"forms\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"a central focus\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"brokerages\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Personally, I have not done so much training on forms myself in over a decade,\\\" saidAnthony Lamacchia, the broker-owner of Massachusetts-basedLamacchia Realty.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much training\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"forms\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"a decade\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \",\\\" saidAnthony Lamacchia\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the broker-owner\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"Massachusetts-basedLamacchia Realty\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Lamacchia, it is essential that his agents and brokers are able to clearly explain and communicate about the forms they are asking clients to sign.\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lamacchia\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"his agents\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"brokers\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"the forms\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Agents in some states, or at some brokerages, are getting these lawyered-up forms thrown at them and no one is explaining to them how to answer questions from clients.\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Agents\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2784}, {\"ngram\": \"some states\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"some brokerages\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2822}, {\"ngram\": \"these lawyered-up forms\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the agents are scared,\\\" Lamacchia said.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the agents\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"Lamacchia\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While learning the forms has been an integral part of many brokerages' training efforts, agents say the role-playing exercises they have engaged in to practice buyer and seller presentations, along with answering buyer and seller questions, have been valuable.\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the forms\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"an integral part\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"many brokerages' training efforts\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3078}, {\"ngram\": \"agents\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"the role-playing exercises\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3117}, {\"ngram\": \"buyer\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"seller presentations\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3181}, {\"ngram\": \"buyer\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"seller questions\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been role-playing how to handle questions from buyers and sellers so that we are armed with answers and know how to handle these situations,\\\" said Brian Huskey, the associate broker of Montana-basedERA American Real Estate.\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3409, \"end\": 3421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Huskey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brian Huskey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Huskey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Huskey\"}, {\"begin\": 3464, \"end\": 3472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999994812984805, \"rank\": 5.185020955612852e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3303}, {\"ngram\": \"buyers\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"sellers\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"answers\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3361}, {\"ngram\": \"these situations\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"the associate broker\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huskey said these training sessions have been mainly confined to his brokerage, which consists of 15 agents, although some have involved the greaterAnywhere Real Estatenetwork, which his firm is a part of.\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huskey\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3493}, {\"ngram\": \"these training sessions\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3522}, {\"ngram\": \"his brokerage\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"15 agents\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3594}, {\"ngram\": \"the greaterAnywhere Real Estatenetwork\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"his firm\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Huskey said he would love to see wider industry collaboration on trainings.\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huskey\", \"from\": 3697, \"to\": 3703}, {\"ngram\": \"wider industry collaboration\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3758}, {\"ngram\": \"trainings\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would be great if we were all on board with the same handful of talking points, because if a consumer goes to four different agents and they all give them different answers, that does not look good for our industry,\\\" Huskey said.\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 4007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 3811, \"to\": 3816}, {\"ngram\": \"the same handful\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3838}, {\"ngram\": \"talking points\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3856}, {\"ngram\": \"a consumer\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3879}, {\"ngram\": \"four different agents\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3909}, {\"ngram\": \"different answers\", \"from\": 3933, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"our industry\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 3992}, {\"ngram\": \"Huskey\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if we all had the same group of talking points to answer questions with, we'd be able to better establish that we are the experts on the industry and home sale transactions.\\\"\", \"from\": 4008, \"to\": 4187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same group\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4041}, {\"ngram\": \"talking points\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4059}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4079}, {\"ngram\": \"the experts\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4142}, {\"ngram\": \"the industry and home sale transactions\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back over on the East Coast, Ruth Kennedy Sudduth - a principal atLandVest Christie's International Real Estatein Boston - said she too is feeling prepared heading into the Aug. 17 implementation date, largely due to the training her brokerage has provided.\", \"from\": 4189, \"to\": 4446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4218, \"end\": 4230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruth_Kennedy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ruth Kennedy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruth_Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruth_Kennedy\"}, {\"begin\": 4303, \"end\": 4309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.999998446273664, \"rank\": 1.5534982373543104e-06, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the East Coast\", \"from\": 4202, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aug. 17 implementation date\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4389}, {\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4418}, {\"ngram\": \"her brokerage\", \"from\": 4419, \"to\": 4432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really commend LandVest and Christie's for the efforts to concertedly not just educate, but listen to the brokers and the agent community about the kinds of issues the business practice changes raise and develop practices that are responsive to that,\\\" Sudduth said.\", \"from\": 4448, \"to\": 4716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LandVest\", \"from\": 4466, \"to\": 4474}, {\"ngram\": \"Christie\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4487}, {\"ngram\": \"the efforts\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4505}, {\"ngram\": \"the brokers\", \"from\": 4553, \"to\": 4564}, {\"ngram\": \"the agent community\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4588}, {\"ngram\": \"the kinds\", \"from\": 4595, \"to\": 4604}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4614}, {\"ngram\": \"the business practice changes\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4644}, {\"ngram\": \"practices\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4672}, {\"ngram\": \"Sudduth\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel really well supported.\\\"\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Sudduth said she is ready to tackle the changes, she is keeping a close watch on how some of these policies may evolve.\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sudduth\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4763}, {\"ngram\": \"the changes\", \"from\": 4792, \"to\": 4803}, {\"ngram\": \"a close watch\", \"from\": 4820, \"to\": 4833}, {\"ngram\": \"these policies\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think everybody needs to think big picture about where the thrust of public policy is headed and try to be consistent with that, and also just try to be transparent with their clients,\\\" Sudduth said.\", \"from\": 4877, \"to\": 5079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 4895}, {\"ngram\": \"big picture\", \"from\": 4911, \"to\": 4922}, {\"ngram\": \"the thrust\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4945}, {\"ngram\": \"public policy\", \"from\": 4949, \"to\": 4962}, {\"ngram\": \"their clients\", \"from\": 5050, \"to\": 5063}, {\"ngram\": \"Sudduth\", \"from\": 5066, \"to\": 5073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although many agents feel prepared and supported by their brokerage,Steve Capezza, the president of white-label brokerageSide, knows that is not the case for others.\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many agents\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5101}, {\"ngram\": \"their brokerage\", \"from\": 5133, \"to\": 5148}, {\"ngram\": \"Steve Capezza\", \"from\": 5149, \"to\": 5162}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 5164, \"to\": 5177}, {\"ngram\": \"white-label brokerageSide\", \"from\": 5181, \"to\": 5206}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 5226, \"to\": 5234}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For Side partners, they will have to deal with these new rules that are going into effect - that said, they have spent months preparing our teams and our partners to be successful and I fully expect them to be,\\\" Capezza said.\", \"from\": 5248, \"to\": 5474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Side partners\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5266}, {\"ngram\": \"these new rules\", \"from\": 5296, \"to\": 5311}, {\"ngram\": \"effect\", \"from\": 5332, \"to\": 5338}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 5368, \"to\": 5374}, {\"ngram\": \"our teams\", \"from\": 5385, \"to\": 5394}, {\"ngram\": \"our partners\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5411}, {\"ngram\": \"Capezza\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course it is a change, so there is always going to be a bit of a change curve, but I think they will move through it relatively smoothly.\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a change\", \"from\": 5493, \"to\": 5501}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 5534, \"to\": 5539}, {\"ngram\": \"a change curve\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, observing the majority of brokerages across the country and the lack of enablement they have put out, there could be a lot of agents that do not know what to do on Aug. 18.\", \"from\": 5618, \"to\": 5801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5651}, {\"ngram\": \"brokerages\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5665}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5684}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5697}, {\"ngram\": \"enablement\", \"from\": 5701, \"to\": 5711}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5746, \"to\": 5751}, {\"ngram\": \"agents\", \"from\": 5755, \"to\": 5761}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 5793, \"to\": 5797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are going to meet with a buy-side prospect through a referral or an online lead, and that conversation is going to be pretty challenging for them.\\\"\", \"from\": 5802, \"to\": 5954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a buy-side prospect\", \"from\": 5830, \"to\": 5849}, {\"ngram\": \"a referral\", \"from\": 5858, \"to\": 5868}, {\"ngram\": \"an online lead\", \"from\": 5872, \"to\": 5886}, {\"ngram\": \"conversation\", \"from\": 5897, \"to\": 5909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While agents acknowledge that this may be the case, many are seeing the changes as a chance for them to truly shine.\", \"from\": 5956, \"to\": 6072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"agents\", \"from\": 5962, \"to\": 5968}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 5998, \"to\": 6006}, {\"ngram\": \"the changes\", \"from\": 6024, \"to\": 6035}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 6039, \"to\": 6047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not something to be scared of,\\\" Huskey said.\", \"from\": 6074, \"to\": 6124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 6084, \"to\": 6093}, {\"ngram\": \"Huskey\", \"from\": 6112, \"to\": 6118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Change is scary, but if you are able to produce your value, you do not have anything to worry about.\", \"from\": 6125, \"to\": 6226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Change\", \"from\": 6126, \"to\": 6132}, {\"ngram\": \"your value\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6184}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 6202, \"to\": 6210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you can show people what they are paying you is sufficient for the service you are providing, you will be fine.\\\"\", \"from\": 6227, \"to\": 6342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6243, \"to\": 6249}, {\"ngram\": \"the service\", \"from\": 6293, \"to\": 6304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your email address will not be published.Required fields are marked* Comment* Name* Email* Website Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment.\", \"from\": 6344, \"to\": 6525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your email address\", \"from\": 6344, \"to\": 6362}, {\"ngram\": \"Required fields\", \"from\": 6385, \"to\": 6400}, {\"ngram\": \"* Comment* Name* Email* Website\", \"from\": 6411, \"to\": 6442}, {\"ngram\": \"my name\", \"from\": 6448, \"to\": 6455}, {\"ngram\": \"email\", \"from\": 6457, \"to\": 6462}, {\"ngram\": \"website\", \"from\": 6468, \"to\": 6475}, {\"ngram\": \"this browser\", \"from\": 6479, \"to\": 6491}, {\"ngram\": \"the next time\", \"from\": 6496, \"to\": 6509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u0394 Mortgage rates remain near 6% as the Fed is expected to cut rates by 25 bps, with experts predicting minimal impact on home loans.\", \"from\": 6531, \"to\": 6664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6571, \"end\": 6574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/